2020-09-07 15:54:42.926 DEBUG 1912 --- [nio-8080-exec-1]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ? offset ?

2020-09-07 15:55:29.339 DEBUG 1912 --- [nio-8080-exec-3]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ? offset ?

2020-09-07 15:55:55.269 DEBUG 1912 --- [nio-8080-exec-4]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ? offset ?

2020-09-07 15:58:42.597 DEBUG 1912 --- [nio-8080-exec-9]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,

        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,

    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,

2020-09-07 16:13:42.793 DEBUG 1912 --- [nio-8080-exec-4]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,
        p.is_deleted ,
        p.description 
    from
        product p 
    left join
        category c 
            on p.category_id = c.id 
    where
        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')     
            or upper(c.name ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')
        )     
    order by
        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?

            or upper(phone_number) like upper(concat('%', ?, '%'))

2020-09-07 16:17:36.438 DEBUG 1912 --- [nio-8080-exec-9]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,
        p.is_deleted ,
        p.description 
    from
        product p 
    left join
        category c 
            on p.category_id = c.id 
    where
        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')     
            or upper(c.name ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')
        )     
    order by
        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?

    select

        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,

2020-09-07 16:58:29.610 DEBUG 18012 --- [nio-8080-exec-6]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        uom,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,
        p.is_deleted ,
        p.description

            on p.category_id = c.id

        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')

        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        uom,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,

        p.description

            on p.category_id = c.id

        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?

2020-09-07 17:02:29.653 DEBUG 18012 --- [nio-8080-exec-6]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

2020-09-07 17:02:42.275 DEBUG 18012 --- [nio-8080-exec-2]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

2020-09-07 17:02:57.424 DEBUG 18012 --- [io-8080-exec-10]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

2020-09-07 17:06:29.304 DEBUG 18012 --- [io-8080-exec-10]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

2020-09-07 17:06:44.108 DEBUG 18012 --- [nio-8080-exec-5]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

2020-09-07 17:06:57.027 DEBUG 18012 --- [nio-8080-exec-7]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        uom,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,
        p.is_deleted ,
        p.description 
    from
        product p 
    left join
        category c 
            on p.category_id = c.id 
    where
        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')     
            or upper(p.code ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')    
            or upper(c.name ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')
        )     
    order by
        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?

2020-09-07 17:08:04.822 DEBUG 18012 --- [io-8080-exec-10]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        cast(o.id as varchar) orderId,
        o.code orderCode,
        o.status,
        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')     
            or upper(sup.name) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or cast(o.total_payment as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

        sup.name supplierName,
        o.quantity,
        o.total_payment totalPayment,
        o.exp_delivery_date expDeliveryDate,
        o.note  
    from
        orders o      
    inner join
        supplier sup 
            on o.supplier_id = sup.id  
    where
        o.is_deleted = false      
        and (
            upper(o.code) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')      
            or upper(o.status) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')  
            or upper(cast(o.supplier_id as varchar)) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')

            or cast(o.quantity as varchar) like concat('%', ?, '%')

            or to_char(o.exp_delivery_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') like concat('%', ?, '%')      
            or upper(o.note) like concat('%', upper(?), '%')
        ) 
    order by
        o.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?

2020-09-07 17:31:10.993 DEBUG 18012 --- [nio-8080-exec-3]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        uom,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,
        p.is_deleted ,
        p.description 
    from
        product p 
    left join
        category c 
            on p.category_id = c.id 
    where
        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')     
            or upper(p.code ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')    
            or upper(c.name ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')
        )     
    order by
        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?

    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        uom,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,

            on p.category_id = c.id

        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')     
            or upper(p.code ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')    
            or upper(c.name ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')
        )

        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?
